 Based on my risk-averse personality, I would prefer to minimize losses and secure a consistent income. In this game, choosing R gives me a higher potential loss if my opponent chooses B. On the other hand, choosing B guarantees me a smaller but consistent payout each round. Since we are playing 75 rounds, the consistency of the B choice adds up significantly over time.

Thus, I would choose B as my strategy to minimize losses and secure a consistent income in this game.
